        lastName - the last name of the customer.
        phoneNumberthe - phone number of the customer.
        driverLicenseNumber - the driver license number of the customer.
        street - the street on which the customer has residence.
        number - the number at which the customer has residence. Can include also letters, floor, apartment and side.
        postalCode - the postal code at which the customer has residence.
        city - the city in which the customer has residence.
